  <div class="card">
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <p><strong>Does Bike Ride Green require an account?</strong><br>No. All ride data stays on your device.</p>
    <p><strong>Can I use the app offline?</strong><br>Yes. The app works completely offline.</p>
    <p><strong>Does the app share my location?</strong><br>No. GPS data is stored locally and never shared.</p>
    <p><strong>How do I delete my data?</strong><br>Delete the app to remove all locally stored data.</p>
